data.description:
When you enter this home , you will be impressed by the light and bright interior, as from the front door you can look straight through to the pool and the gold course. Built in 1998, right on the first hole of the course, this is a VERY attractive home. Nice pool surrounded by trees for privacy. The home itself has a very large living room area, a separate cozy family room, kitchen, master suite with sliders opening up to pool area, a bathroom with shower and jetted tub, double sinks and LARGE walk in closets.  Two more bedrooms, two car garage. Home situated on a cul de sac, with only four more houses on this quiet street yet close to the clubhouse.Southern Woods always seems so much more pleasant to the eye than other areas here. A NEW roof in 2019 with transferable warranty, new pool screening and newer AC (5 yrs old).
This home really deserves a look, you will be pleasantly surprised. Sellers are motivated, so bring your buyers please!
